{"tid":487773,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"like係中意 dislike係唔中意 play係玩 display點解唔係唔玩？？？？？？？","createTime":"2017-12-03T05:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T08:45:56.000Z","uid":34714,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"825cc7c1a0b97ab2b98a1fa0f861bfebd3c9e1a8","tid":487773,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T05:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76647a763ec3ca987504f3f130c1dabbc998cb2d","tid":487773,"uid":152376,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T05:50:40.000Z","msg":"display 淨係顯示 唔洗玩"},{"pid":"4780bbfa0f705c45f18dbeec8e88b0dae1a0ffe2","tid":487773,"uid":36434,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>display 淨係顯示 唔洗玩</blockquote><br />\n哈"},{"pid":"f6c9cf088156d2f97fbd2925cbec567c7f0d4944","tid":487773,"uid":71166,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T01:32:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>display 淨係顯示 唔洗玩</blockquote><br />\n哈</blockquote><br />\n密瓜"},{"pid":"0e3152e5049d8d5652b372e22e896be7c290675c","tid":487773,"uid":3571,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T01:48:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4622c9d2ffb58c519bc8b2556ac5fffb19356836","tid":487773,"uid":9699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T01:56:49.000Z","msg":"等睇肥屍回覆"},{"pid":"cb8d3c7c6c277beafb8c90a5780cb65a5c55ae09","tid":487773,"uid":79190,"like":113,"dislike":3,"score":110,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T02:48:50.000Z","msg":"要答樓主嘅問題<br />\n首先要理解左小小關於英語嘅語源同背景先<br />\n<br />\n英語主要係由古代英語，拉丁文同古代法語構成嘅<br />\n古代英語屬於日耳曼語系入面嘅其中一門語言<br />\n講嘅人都係係英格蘭同威爾士上面嘅原住民<br />\n所以古代英語係英國本身嘅語言<br />\n但係由於英國原住民嘅文明水平唔高，所以古代英語所表述嘅詞彙一直只係限制係同生活有關嘅元素上，例如衣食住行，玩等等<br />\n<br />\n呢種情況直到羅馬人入侵英國先有改善，羅馬人講拉丁文，佢地統治英國之後<br />\n傳入左拉丁文入面比較學術嘅concept，一啲比較學術嘅用語，其實到而家都係拉丁文黎，例如bio入面好多生物嘅名，星座嘅語源等<br />\n就算之後羅馬人走左，拉丁文都係英國同歐洲大陸溝通嘅「雅言」之一，上流社會一定識<br />\n<br />\n到最後係法語，有讀過西史一定直到英國曾經係羅馬人走左之後，比逃離法國嘅法國貴族統治過，因此有一段時間，英國嘅王室同上流社會都只係講法文而唔會講古代英文。到最後，法文嘅一啲詞彙就留左係英文入面啦。<br />\n<br />\n答翻樓主條問題<br />\n係下面條link 我地見到<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com/browse/play?s=t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dictionary.com%2Fbrowse%2Fplay%3Fs%3Dt&d=7yrBVEiWxAMk2TXQ7%2BGX27IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=c17e79ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dictionary.com/browse/play?s=t</a><br />\nPlay 嘅語源係古代英文pleye, 同樣係玩嘅意思<br />\n維基可以印證呢樣嘢 <a href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/play\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wiktionary.org%2Fwiki%2Fplay&d=7yrBVEiWxAMk2TXQ7%2BGX27IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8e35ba01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/play</a><br />\n<br />\n至於dis，係拉丁文流傳入英文嘅借詞，係代表唔係，非某樣嘢嘅前綴，見link<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com/browse/dis-?s=t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dictionary.com%2Fbrowse%2Fdis-%3Fs%3Dt&d=7yrBVEiWxAMk2TXQ7%2BGX27IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=cae51e19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dictionary.com/browse/dis-?s=t</a><br />\n<br />\n最後display 就比較複雜<br />\n首先睇呢條link <a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com/browse/display?s=t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dictionary.com%2Fbrowse%2Fdisplay%3Fs%3Dt&d=7yrBVEiWxAMk2TXQ7%2BGX27IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e4d07ff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dictionary.com/browse/display?s=t</a><br />\n佢嘅語源首先係由拉丁文 displicāre 轉化而黎<br />\nplicāre 係摺左fold嘅意思 （<a href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/plico#Latin）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wiktionary.org%2Fwiki%2Fplico%23Latin%EF%BC%89&d=7yrBVEiWxAMk2TXQ7%2BGX27IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=c7e90fd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/plico#Latin）</a><br />\n順理成章displicāre就係unfold 而unfold就即係展示啦,（<a href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/desploiier#Old_French）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wiktionary.org%2Fwiki%2Fdesploiier%23Old_French%EF%BC%89&d=7yrBVEiWxAMk2TXQ7%2BGX27IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=041d9db9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/desploiier#Old_French）</a><br />\n再跟住古代法語先吸收左拉丁文（法國曾經都係羅馬帝國領土）<br />\n變成despleier，再跟住由古代英文吸收變成 desplayen<br />\n留意返desplayen 其實同古代英文pleye 相似<br />\n因此到最後就變成而家嘅英文display 啦<br />\n只能說此play非彼play"},{"pid":"c13906a99f011c551e553a192cfac9fa81f495da","tid":487773,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T02:50:51.000Z","msg":"鍾意呀,中乜撚野呀"},{"pid":"6e0625d4a9ea9199abbe902415d7ed570e76cd4e","tid":487773,"uid":10981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T03:22:19.000Z","msg":"你係咪好悶"},{"pid":"62459a2523e2d66f5770274b0534039fc2c261c4","tid":487773,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T03:45:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要答樓主嘅問題<br />\n首先要理解左小小關於英語嘅語源同背景先<br />\n<br />\n英語主要係由古代英語，拉丁文同古代法語構成嘅<br />\n古代英語屬於日耳曼語系入面嘅其中一門語言<br />\n講嘅人都係係英格蘭同威爾士上面嘅原住民<br />\n所以古代英語係英國本身嘅語言<br />\n但係由於英國原住民嘅文明水平唔高，所以古代英語所表述嘅詞彙一直只係限制係同生活有關嘅元素上，例如衣食住行，玩等等<br />\n<br />\n呢種情況直到羅馬人入侵英國先有改善，羅馬人講拉丁文，佢地統治英國之後<br />\n傳入左拉丁文入面比較學術嘅concept，一啲比較學術嘅用語，其實到而家都係拉丁文黎，例如bio入面好多生物嘅名，星座嘅語源等<br />\n就算之後羅馬人走左，拉丁文都係英國同歐洲大陸溝通嘅「雅言」之一，上流社會一定識<br />\n<br />\n到最後係法語，有讀過西史一定直到英國曾經係羅馬人走左之後，比逃離法國嘅法國貴族統治過，因此有一段時間，英國嘅王室同上流社會都只係講法文而唔會講古代英文。到最後，法文嘅一啲詞彙就留左係英文入面啦。<br />\n<br />\n答翻樓主條問題<br />\n係下面條link 我地見到<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com/browse/play?s=t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dictionary.com%2Fbrowse%2Fplay%3Fs%3Dt&d=7yrBVEiWxAMk2TXQ7%2BGX27IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=c17e79ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dictionary.com/browse/play?s=t</a><br />\nPlay 嘅語源係古代英文pleye, 同樣係玩嘅意思<br />\n維基可以印證呢樣嘢 <a href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/play\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wiktionary.org%2Fwiki%2Fplay&d=7yrBVEiWxAMk2TXQ7%2BGX27IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8e35ba01\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/play</a><br />\n<br />\n至於dis，係拉丁文流傳入英文嘅借詞，係代表唔係，非某樣嘢嘅前綴，見link<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com/browse/dis-?s=t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dictionary.com%2Fbrowse%2Fdis-%3Fs%3Dt&d=7yrBVEiWxAMk2TXQ7%2BGX27IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=cae51e19\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dictionary.com/browse/dis-?s=t</a><br />\n<br />\n最後display 就比較複雜<br />\n首先睇呢條link <a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com/browse/display?s=t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dictionary.com%2Fbrowse%2Fdisplay%3Fs%3Dt&d=7yrBVEiWxAMk2TXQ7%2BGX27IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e4d07ff7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dictionary.com/browse/display?s=t</a><br />\n佢嘅語源首先係由拉丁文 displicāre 轉化而黎<br />\nplicāre 係摺左fold嘅意思 （<a href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/plico#Latin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wiktionary.org%2Fwiki%2Fplico%23Latin&d=7yrBVEiWxAMk2TXQ7%2BGX27IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=1959a3e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/plico#Latin</a>）<br />\n順理成章displicāre就係unfold 而unfold就即係展示啦,（<a href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/desploiier#Old_French\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wiktionary.org%2Fwiki%2Fdesploiier%23Old_French&d=7yrBVEiWxAMk2TXQ7%2BGX27IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=c6b1c3e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/desploiier#Old_French</a>）<br />\n再跟住古代法語先吸收左拉丁文（法國曾經都係羅馬帝國領土）<br />\n變成despleier，再跟住由古代英文吸收變成 desplayen<br />\n留意返desplayen 其實同古代英文pleye 相似<br />\n因此到最後就變成而家嘅英文display 啦<br />\n只能說此play非彼play</blockquote><br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d986662b2360abb0c39adbebdbd0b90ff24d13","tid":487773,"uid":24523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T03:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要答樓主嘅問題<br />\n首先要理解左小小關於英語嘅語源同背景先<br />\n<br />\n英語主要係由古代英語，拉丁文同古代法語構成嘅<br />\n古代英語屬於日耳曼語系入面嘅其中一門語言<br />\n講嘅人都係係